      "date": "2012-11-25 19:44:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a68954f4-3734-11e2-8203-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
